String generateHospitalAbout(String name, String location) {
  return '$name is a trusted healthcare institution located in $location, committed to providing high-quality medical services with compassion and care. Our hospital offers a wide range of medical specialties, equipped with modern facilities and an experienced team of doctors, nurses, and staff dedicated to patient well-being.\n\n'
      'At $name, we prioritize patient safety, advanced diagnostics, and affordable treatment. Whether it\'s routine checkups, emergency care, or specialized procedures, we strive to serve the community of $location with excellence and integrity.';
}
